\sqrt{31-8\sqrt{15}}+\sqrt{31+8\sqrt{15}}
31 + 8\sqrt{15} = (a + b\sqrt{15})^2 = (a^2 + 15b^2) + 2ab\sqrt{15}
a
b
a = 4
b = 1
\begin{align}(4 + \sqrt{15})^2 &= 16 + 15 + 8 \sqrt{15} \\ &= 31 + 8 \sqrt{15}\end{align}
\begin{align}(4 - \sqrt{15})^2 &= 16 + 15 - 8 \sqrt{15} \\ &= 31 - 8 \sqrt{15}\end{align}
\begin{align}\sqrt{31-8\sqrt{15}}+\sqrt{31+8\sqrt{15}} &= \sqrt{(4 - \sqrt{15})^2} + \sqrt{(4 + \sqrt{15})^2} \\ &= 4 - \sqrt{15} + 4 + \sqrt{15} \\  &= 8\end{align}
(\sqrt{31-8\sqrt{15}}+\sqrt{31+8\sqrt{15}})^2 = (31-8\sqrt{15}) + (31+8\sqrt{15}) + 2\sqrt{31^2-64.15} = 64
8
u = \pm 8
 u = \sqrt{31 -8 \sqrt{15}} + \sqrt{31 + 8 \sqrt{15}} 
 u^2 = 31 - 8 \sqrt{15} + 31 + 8 \sqrt{15} + 2 \sqrt{31^2 - 8^2 \cdot 15}     = 62 + 2 \cdot 1 = 64 
 \sqrt{31 -8 \sqrt{15}} + \sqrt{31 + 8 \sqrt{15}} = 8 
a=31+8\sqrt {15}, b=31-8\sqrt {15}
a+b=62
ab=31^2-15\cdot 64=31^2-30\cdot32=1
